        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Value is calculated for basmati rice that is globally produced. The value is scaled from the respective Indian value considering the fact that circa 70% of the global basmati rice production takes place in India. This yields a total of 12.52 million tonnes of basmati rice produced globally. 
Reference: Cultivation and Export of Basmati Rice from India, accessed online at: https://www.gktoday.in/gk/cultivation-and-export-of-basmati-rice-from-india/</productionVolumeComment>
